                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Longitudinally polarized protons on a",
                " liquid deuterium target.  Neutrons produced at 0 deg.",
                " collimated and passed through magnetic fields to",
                " rotate the spins to L-type in either clockwise or",
                " counterclockwise direction.  Spin orientations",
                " reversed every few hours to reduce systematic effects",
                " in cross section difference."
              ]
            }
          ],
